<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="10000000t" end="60000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"></p>
<p begin="60000000t" end="110000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">翻譯:地字一號  後期:小聖  BDRip:TNTI</p>
<p begin="112500000t" end="144600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">最高級的紅茶泡好了  和真先生</p>
<p begin="148900000t" end="152300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">嗯～</p>
<p begin="208000000t" end="217200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">這是白開水呀</p>
<p begin="234500000t" end="255300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">哎呀  我真是不小心</p>
<p begin="260500000t" end="283900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">難不成  你把紅茶淨化掉了嗎</p>
<p begin="291200000t" end="310000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">對不起啦  和真先生</p>
<p begin="314000000t" end="327700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">重新泡就好了</p>
<p begin="330800000t" end="342900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">謝謝你  阿庫婭</p>
<p begin="342900000t" end="355400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">不過我還是會喝的</p>
<p begin="376700000t" end="391300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">嗯～白開水</p>
<p begin="397300000t" end="414400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">好噁心</p>
<p begin="1330200000t" end="1369900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">向妄自尊大的廢柴發出邀請!</p>
<p begin="1341000000t" end="1355500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">前幾天的事情是我不好</p>
<p begin="1360500000t" end="1385500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">所以  請你變回原本的和真吧</p>
<p begin="1389000000t" end="1399000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">前幾天的事?</p>
<p begin="1406500000t" end="1441500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">什麼叫  聖劍EX咖哩棒啊!</p>
<p begin="1449500000t" end="1467500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">哦  那點小事嗎</p>
<p begin="1473500000t" end="1489000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">俗話說  和氣生財嘛</p>
<p begin="1494500000t" end="1518000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">比起那種事  惠惠要不要也來喝杯茶</p>
<p begin="1526500000t" end="1542000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">我搞到了很不錯的茶葉哦</p>
<p begin="1561000000t" end="1576000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">都是我不好</p>
<p begin="1577500000t" end="1602500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">求你了  請變回原本的和真吧</p>
<p begin="1605500000t" end="1631500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">現在的和真好噁心啊</p>
<p begin="1631500000t" end="1647000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">從剛才起就在胡說什麼啊</p>
<p begin="1652000000t" end="1667500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">我一直都是這樣啊</p>
<p begin="1675000000t" end="1707000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">最高級的紅茶泡好了哦  和真先生</p>
<p begin="1750000000t" end="1759500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">白開水呀</p>
<p begin="1763000000t" end="1790000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">哈哈  又淨化掉了嗎</p>
<p begin="1794500000t" end="1841000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">哎呀  我真是不小心  呼呼</p>
<p begin="1847500000t" end="1870500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">沒事  重新泡就好了</p>
<p begin="1875500000t" end="1885000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">謝謝你  阿庫婭</p>
<p begin="1889000000t" end="1903000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">我還是會喝的</p>
<p begin="1916000000t" end="1924500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">其實…</p>
<p begin="1933000000t" end="1952000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">那個該死的小蘿莉</p>
<p begin="1954500000t" end="1973000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">等她回來之後我一定要扒光她</p>
<p begin="1974500000t" end="1997500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">絕對  絕對的</p>
<p begin="1999500000t" end="2014000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">要做出讓不服輸的她</p>
<p begin="2015000000t" end="2044500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">都哭著說「請放過我」的事情</p>
<p begin="2048500000t" end="2081000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">那個…關於讓惠惠都哭著求饒的事…</p>
<p begin="2081000000t" end="2089500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">能詳細說說嗎</p>
<p begin="2092000000t" end="2108500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">大清早的吵什麼啊</p>
<p begin="2112500000t" end="2133500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">你們就不能像我一樣冷靜嗎</p>
<p begin="2140500000t" end="2161000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">看看我  自從昨天回到家裡</p>
<p begin="2161000000t" end="2187500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">除了洗澡就沒離開過這個地方</p>
<p begin="2190500000t" end="2223500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">在這裡躺了一整天的廢人有什麼資格說我</p>
<p begin="2225500000t" end="2251500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">可惡  我絕不饒她</p>
<p begin="2253500000t" end="2285500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">我已經忍不住想看到她哭著求饒的樣子了</p>
<p begin="2289500000t" end="2314500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">關於那個哭著求饒的事…請詳細說說</p>
<p begin="2344500000t" end="2381500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">你回來了嗎  惠惠</p>
<p begin="2358000000t" end="2365000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">詳細說說</p>
<p begin="2397500000t" end="2428000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">你以為是那個腦袋有問題的紅魔族女孩嗎</p>
<p begin="2430500000t" end="2450000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">太遺憾了  是吾啊</p>
<p begin="2455000000t" end="2497000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">代替廢材店主  聰明的吾來和你談生意了</p>
<p begin="2501000000t" end="2527500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">對吾的登場  高興得跪倒在地吧</p>
<p begin="2530500000t" end="2554000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">快把你打算賣給本店的商品拿出來看看</p>
<p begin="2571490000t" end="2583500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">我說…</p>
<p begin="2588500000t" end="2610000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">你是怎麼進到這房子裡來的</p>
<p begin="2613990000t" end="2635500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">那個不成氣候的東西嗎</p>
<p begin="2639500000t" end="2663000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">什麼  原來那是結界啊</p>
<p begin="2668000000t" end="2692000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">因為實在太過孱弱</p>
<p begin="2695000000t" end="2731000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">吾還以為是哪個新手大司祭張開的失敗作</p>
<p begin="2737000000t" end="2745000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">哎呀  抱歉</p>
<p begin="2748500000t" end="2768000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">超強的吾只是經過了一下</p>
<p begin="2769500000t" end="2793500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">好像就弄壞了</p>
<p begin="2830000000t" end="2871500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">哎呀  您的身體到處都在潰散呢</p>
<p begin="2872500000t" end="2890000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">超強的惡魔先生</p>
<p begin="2897500000t" end="2908000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">怎麼回事啊</p>
<p begin="2911000000t" end="2939500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">我記得你是地獄的公爵來著吧</p>
<p begin="2941500000t" end="2973500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">那種程度的結界就變成這樣了嗎</p>
<p begin="2987000000t" end="3004000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">反正這個身體也只是土塊而已</p>
<p begin="3008500000t" end="3023500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">吾隨時都可以製造出替代品</p>
<p begin="3026500000t" end="3069000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">吾只是突然對外面的輕薄結界產生了興趣</p>
<p begin="3074000000t" end="3110500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">以菜鳥大祭司所張設的結界而言算是不錯了吧</p>
<p begin="3112000000t" end="3155500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">嗯  對人類的  菜鳥大司祭來說</p>
<p begin="3171000000t" end="3190000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">喂  你們冷靜下來</p>
<p begin="3210500000t" end="3218500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">吶  和真</p>
<p begin="3218500000t" end="3223000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">怎麼了</p>
<p begin="3224500000t" end="3242000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">你製作暖桌之類的東西</p>
<p begin="3243500000t" end="3263500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">難道是為了和這傢伙做生意嗎</p>
<p begin="3267000000t" end="3273500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">是啊</p>
<p begin="3275000000t" end="3319500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">和靠吸食人類的負面情緒勉強生存的這種害蟲嗎</p>
<p begin="3318000000t" end="3332500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">你和他的表情也差不多啊</p>
<p begin="3324000000t" end="3355500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">不要啦  這個玩笑一點也不好笑</p>
<p begin="3365000000t" end="3373000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">不不  你已經在笑了</p>
<p begin="3373000000t" end="3417500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">我們惡魔很重視契約  很感謝你能信任我</p>
<p begin="3421500000t" end="3442000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">說什麼只要相信就能幸福</p>
<p begin="3444500000t" end="3460500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">專門欺騙善良的人</p>
<p begin="3463500000t" end="3483000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">用可疑的口號召集教徒</p>
<p begin="3483000000t" end="3493000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">表面上說是捐贈</p>
<p begin="3493000000t" end="3522000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">其實是賺取不義之財的欺詐團伙可不一樣</p>
<p begin="3528000000t" end="3548000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">他們的口號是什麼來著</p>
<p begin="3561000000t" end="3569500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">對了</p>
<p begin="3577000000t" end="3614000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">神一直都在注視著你…嗎</p>
<p begin="3618500000t" end="3673500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">原來如此  吾輩可是看到他們說的那個神了哦</p>
<p begin="3682000000t" end="3703000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">前幾天因為偷窺被抓住的</p>
<p begin="3703500000t" end="3739000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">用熱情的目光注視著澡堂和廁所的男人</p>
<p begin="3742500000t" end="3755000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">原來是神嗎</p>
<p begin="3807500000t" end="3828500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">神聖驅魔!</p>
<p begin="3828500000t" end="3832500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">危險</p>
<p begin="3857500000t" end="3871000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">華麗蛻皮!</p>
<p begin="3940000000t" end="3961000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">就是這個吧  這就是你的本體吧</p>
<p begin="3962500000t" end="3993500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">怎麼辦呢  怎麼處理這個東西呢</p>
<p begin="3995500000t" end="4019500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">哈哈  就算你破壞了這個假面…</p>
<p begin="4020000000t" end="4047000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">喂  我還在說話不要拿我面具</p>
<p begin="4047000000t" end="4057000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">身體會潰散掉的</p>
<p begin="4051500000t" end="4065000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">兩位冷靜</p>
<p begin="4057000000t" end="4078500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">讓我把台詞說完啊</p>
<p begin="4083000000t" end="4091500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">美好世界</p>
<p begin="4099000000t" end="4115000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">那麼開始談生意吧</p>
<p begin="4120500000t" end="4161800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">按照合約  你將獲得利潤的十分之一</p>
<p begin="4172500000t" end="4209800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">怎麼樣  打不打算賣這些東西的知識產權</p>
<p begin="4219800000t" end="4236500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">我花三億厄里斯來買</p>
<p begin="4237800000t" end="4250500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">三億?</p>
<p begin="4253600000t" end="4282700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">這個價格的話  不用工作也能活一輩子了</p>
<p begin="4288500000t" end="4305600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">換算成每個月的金額的話</p>
<p begin="4305600000t" end="4319300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">一個月是一百萬厄里斯</p>
<p begin="4321000000t" end="4337600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">一個月一百萬</p>
<p begin="4340500000t" end="4359300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">難以保證以後也能賣得好</p>
<p begin="4361600000t" end="4379300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">是不是直接拿三億比較好</p>
<p begin="4379900000t" end="4417000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">不  是不用在意存款減少的每月一百萬嗎</p>
<p begin="4439900000t" end="4455900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">你就慢慢思考吧</p>
<p begin="4441000000t" end="4490200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">每個月一百萬…高級燒酒  高級燒酒</p>
<p begin="4459300000t" end="4493600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">那麼吾輩很擔心店裡的情況  先回去了</p>
<p begin="4501600000t" end="4530700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">我神聖的家裡都充滿惡臭了</p>
<p begin="4530700000t" end="4554700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">你快出去  滾出去</p>
<p begin="4612500000t" end="4627900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">白開水呢  白開水</p>
<p begin="4629600000t" end="4647900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">哎呀  都怪我</p>
<p begin="4663900000t" end="4687900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">那之後  他們兩個就一直是那副德性了</p>
<p begin="4691900000t" end="4713000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">我明白他們為何要裝高貴了</p>
<p begin="4719300000t" end="4740500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">好吧  有錢確實是件好事</p>
<p begin="4745600000t" end="4764500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">那麼  我們再去討伐任務吧</p>
<p begin="4768500000t" end="4793000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">咦  我才不要  你在說什麼啊</p>
<p begin="4798700000t" end="4834200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">都成有錢人了  為什麼還得要工作啊</p>
<p begin="4860500000t" end="4896500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">況且就算是有裝備有計劃</p>
<p begin="4896500000t" end="4909600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">我還是摔斷了脖子死掉了哦</p>
<p begin="4914200000t" end="4939900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">決定了  以後我要靠做生意過活</p>
<p begin="4942700000t" end="4963300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">脫離冒險者這種危險的工作</p>
<p begin="4963300000t" end="4983300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">度過安穩的人生</p>
<p begin="4986700000t" end="4999300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">和真先生</p>
