<p begin="8998200000t" end="9024500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">你有你的運氣  我有我的方法</p>
<p begin="9031300000t" end="9039900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">祝福!</p>
<p begin="9051300000t" end="9062700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">啊  好卑鄙</p>
<p begin="9062700000t" end="9079900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">居然用魔法提高運氣</p>
<p begin="9079900000t" end="9099900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">運氣也是實力的一種</p>
<p begin="9101600000t" end="9122200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">所以魔法的實力也是一種運氣吧</p>
<p begin="9125600000t" end="9154700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">那麼開始吧  石頭剪刀布</p>
<p begin="9158700000t" end="9174700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">為什麼啊</p>
<p begin="9178200000t" end="9213000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">我從小到大猜拳沒輸過呢</p>
<p begin="9213000000t" end="9233000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">卑鄙小人  那是什麼  太狡猾了</p>
<p begin="9233000000t" end="9256500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">你這是作弊  作弊能力啊</p>
<p begin="9258700000t" end="9284500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">你天生就是特殊能力者嗎</p>
<p begin="9287900000t" end="9331300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">那麼你得到我這個恩惠的事就無效了</p>
<p begin="9331300000t" end="9355300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">快放我回去  放我回天界去</p>
<p begin="9356300000t" end="9367900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">你這卑鄙的作弊者</p>
<p begin="9367900000t" end="9383900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">你這可惡的婊子</p>
<p begin="9384500000t" end="9414200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">我的特殊能力就是猜拳能贏嗎</p>
<p begin="9414200000t" end="9448500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">你傻不傻啊  這種能力怎麼與怪物戰鬥啊</p>
<p begin="9449600000t" end="9461600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">可是…</p>
<p begin="9463900000t" end="9508500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">我最生氣的  是你居然自稱恩惠</p>
<p begin="9511300000t" end="9535900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">你開什麼玩笑  你憑什麼叫恩惠</p>
<p begin="9538200000t" end="9562200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">要是能把你退貨  換一個特殊能力來的話</p>
<p begin="9562700000t" end="9581000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">我早就退貨了</p>
<p begin="9619300000t" end="9641000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">和真說了不該說的話</p>
<p begin="9646200000t" end="9669600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">不要  不要拉我了</p>
<p begin="9679300000t" end="9709000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">去往阿爾坎雷堤亞  出發</p>
<p begin="10379300000t" end="10412500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">對貴族小姐來說  也是充滿了新奇嗎</p>
<p begin="10474200000t" end="10491900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">還是逗之助可愛一點</p>
<p begin="10504500000t" end="10542700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">沒想到到這個世界後  還能像這樣出發旅遊呢</p>
<p begin="10557000000t" end="10565600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">還不錯</p>
<p begin="10570700000t" end="10589000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">和真</p>
<p begin="10591900000t" end="10615300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">我的屁股好痛喔</p>
<p begin="10621000000t" end="10653600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">差不多該有人跟我換一下位子了吧</p>
<p begin="10677600000t" end="10700500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">等停下來休息的時候我再和你交換</p>
<p begin="10702700000t" end="10720500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">你就忍耐到那個時候吧</p>
<p begin="10724500000t" end="10746200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">怎麼能這樣</p>
<p begin="10809600000t" end="10821000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">千里眼</p>
<p begin="10854200000t" end="10863300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">那是什麼</p>
<p begin="10867900000t" end="10912500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">不好意思  那邊好像有一陣煙塵往這邊過來了</p>
<p begin="10917600000t" end="10930200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">大叔知不知道那是什麼啊</p>
<p begin="10942200000t" end="10969600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">誰知道呢  我可看不見</p>
<p begin="10972500000t" end="10995900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">不過說到會在這一帶揚起煙塵的生物</p>
<p begin="10998700000t" end="11022200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">大概就是蜥蜴奔跑者的群落了吧</p>
<p begin="11031300000t" end="11068500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">不過聽說領頭的公主蜥蜴前幾天已經被打倒了</p>
<p begin="11070700000t" end="11109000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">一定是沙塵鯨魚在噴沙塵吧</p>
<p begin="11110700000t" end="11141000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">至於其它的  好像就只剩下「跑跳鷹鳶」了吧</p>
<p begin="11141600000t" end="11149600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">跑跳鷹鳶?</p>
<p begin="11141600000t" end="11149600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">註：「跳」與「鷹鳶」同音</p>
<p begin="11154200000t" end="11175300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">客人  這可不是冷笑話哦</p>
<p begin="11177600000t" end="11201000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">那可是相當危險的怪物</p>
<p begin="11203900000t" end="11224500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">一到繁殖期  為了吸引雌鳥的注意</p>
<p begin="11224500000t" end="11269000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">雄鳥之間會進行比拼誰更勇敢的試膽競速比賽</p>
<p begin="11271900000t" end="11292500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">它們會找堅硬的目標衝過去</p>
<p begin="11292500000t" end="11309000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">在差一點撞上之前躲開</p>
<p begin="11318200000t" end="11355900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">不過一定會去撞附近的岩石的  所以沒問題</p>
<p begin="11358700000t" end="11369600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">那我就放心了</p>
<p begin="11442700000t" end="11472500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">不過好像氣勢十足地朝這邊來了誒</p>
<p begin="11479300000t" end="11506700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">哦  那就是跑跳鷹鳶了</p>
<p begin="11509000000t" end="11542200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">不過居然會朝我們衝過來  真是太奇怪了</p>
<p begin="11542200000t" end="11609000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">難道車隊裡有裝了堅硬的亞德曼礦石的車嗎</p>
<p begin="11626700000t" end="11658200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">好像朝這邊…應該說朝我們的車來了</p>
<p begin="11665600000t" end="11692500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">亞德曼礦石般的硬度…</p>
<p begin="11700500000t" end="11705600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">喂  達克…</p>
<p begin="11705600000t" end="11716500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">和真和真</p>
<p begin="11719300000t" end="11750700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">有速度超快的怪物朝我們衝過來了</p>
<p begin="11753600000t" end="11777600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">應該說它們都在看我啊</p>
<p begin="11782700000t" end="11797600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">好熱情的視線啊</p>
<p begin="11804500000t" end="11814700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">是你啊!</p>
<p begin="11815300000t" end="11834200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">客人  我要停車了</p>
<p begin="11838200000t" end="11872500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">護衛的冒險者會保護馬車和客人們的</p>
<p begin="11881000000t" end="11905000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">不好意思  我家的十字騎士太硬了</p>
<p begin="11911300000t" end="11935900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">喂  達克尼斯  那些怪物是衝著你來的</p>
<p begin="11937600000t" end="11961600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">聽說它們喜歡朝著堅硬的東西衝刺</p>
<p begin="11963900000t" end="11987900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">它們的目標是你那身硬梆梆的肌肉</p>
<p begin="11991300000t" end="11998200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">喂  和真</p>
<p begin="12002700000t" end="12019300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">我好歹也算是少女</p>
<p begin="12023300000t" end="12038700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">不要說我的肌肉硬梆梆</p>
<p begin="12044500000t" end="12047900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">應該是因為那個吧</p>
<p begin="12053000000t" end="12083300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">我的鎧甲是含有少量亞達曼礦石的特別訂製品</p>
<p begin="12092500000t" end="12109600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">它們一定是因為這樣才會朝我衝過來的</p>
<p begin="12121600000t" end="12145600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">真的啦  所以不要這樣看我</p>
<p begin="12147300000t" end="12167300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">我的身體沒有那麼硬啊</p>
<p begin="12171300000t" end="12185600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">惠惠  阿庫婭  該我們上場了</p>
<p begin="12193600000t" end="12211300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">雖然本來不該我們戰鬥</p>
<p begin="12213600000t" end="12232500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">但這次的敵人是我們吸引過來的</p>
<p begin="12234700000t" end="12255900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">自己的屁股必須自己擦乾淨才行</p>
<p begin="12260500000t" end="12274700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">我也來幫忙</p>
<p begin="12276500000t" end="12302200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">維茲就在車上保護車夫</p>
<p begin="12308500000t" end="12314200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">是</p>
<p begin="12318700000t" end="12326200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">客人!</p>
<p begin="12327300000t" end="12345600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">客人您是付過錢的</p>
<p begin="12349600000t" end="12358700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">請躲在安全的地方</p>
<p begin="12363300000t" end="12386700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">對不起  我的夥伴是這事的起因</p>
<p begin="12400500000t" end="12423900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">各位冒險者們  拜託了</p>
<p begin="12429600000t" end="12434700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">就…</p>
<p begin="12434700000t" end="12443900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">包在…</p>
<p begin="12443900000t" end="12451300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">我們…</p>
<p begin="12451300000t" end="12458200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">身上吧</p>
<p begin="12510700000t" end="12529000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">惠惠準備使用爆裂魔法</p>
<p begin="12537000000t" end="12549000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">明白了</p>
<p begin="12562200000t" end="12572500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">那邊的那個十字騎士</p>
<p begin="12575300000t" end="12600500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">你不是護衛  退下吧</p>
<p begin="12607900000t" end="12643900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">怪物們朝著那個十字騎士衝過去了…</p>
<p begin="12653000000t" end="12662700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">那是「誘餌」吧</p>
<p begin="12669000000t" end="12684500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">那個十字騎士用的那招叫作「誘餌」</p>
<p begin="12685600000t" end="12699900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">是能夠吸引敵人的技能</p>
<p begin="12703300000t" end="12741600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">那個十字騎士明明不是護衛  卻吸引了敵人</p>
<p begin="12747300000t" end="12767900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">非常抱歉  她並沒有用那種技能</p>
<p begin="12770200000t" end="12795900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">面對這麼多敵人依然沒有絲毫退意</p>
<p begin="12799900000t" end="12811300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">真是太勇敢了!</p>
<p begin="12817000000t" end="12843900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">非常抱歉  理由大概和你想的完全不同</p>
<p begin="12851300000t" end="12860500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">她只是客人</p>
<p begin="12860500000t" end="12892500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">怎麼能讓沒有收護衛費的冒險者面對危險</p>
<p begin="12895300000t" end="12907900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">讓我掩護你吧</p>
<p begin="12910700000t" end="12919900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">束縛!</p>
<p begin="12920500000t" end="12926200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">什麼</p>
<p begin="13004500000t" end="13011300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">怎麼會…</p>
<p begin="13014200000t" end="13061000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">因為怕我使用束縛技能後  成為怪物的目標</p>
<p begin="13061000000t" end="13077000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">幫我擋住了嗎</p>
<p begin="13079300000t" end="13097000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">對不起  明明想掩護你</p>
<p begin="13099900000t" end="13113600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">卻反而添了麻煩</p>
<p begin="13116500000t" end="13150700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">原諒我  原諒我啊</p>
<p begin="13163900000t" end="13177600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">對不起</p>
<p begin="13181000000t" end="13194200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">我的夥伴真是對不起大家</p>
<p begin="13194200000t" end="13234700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">我家的變態真的對不起大家了!</p>
<p begin="13345600000t" end="13392700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">何も言わず　家を出て</p>
<p begin="13345600000t" end="13392700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">一聲不吭  離家而去</p>
<p begin="13398500000t" end="13445200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">こんなとこまで　来たけれど</p>
<p begin="13398500000t" end="13445200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">一個人來到了  這樣的地方</p>
<p begin="13451500000t" end="13497800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">日暮れと共に　泣き虫が</p>
<p begin="13451500000t" end="13497800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">夕陽西下時分  愛哭的孩子</p>
<p begin="13504100000t" end="13547400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">心細いと　へそを掻く</p>
<p begin="13504100000t" end="13547400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">心中感到害怕  流下了眼淚</p>
<p begin="13556200000t" end="13605000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">赤く染まる　町の空を</p>
<p begin="13556200000t" end="13605000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">染成深紅色的  小鎮的天空</p>
<p begin="13609200000t" end="13653400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">鴉が鳴いて　行き過ぎる</p>
<p begin="13609200000t" end="13653400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">烏鴉尖聲鳴叫  從頭頂飛過</p>
<p begin="13661300000t" end="13709300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">道に延びる　長い影が</p>
<p begin="13661300000t" end="13709300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">道路上拉長的  瘦長的影子</p>
<p begin="13714300000t" end="13759300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">速く帰ろと　袖を引く</p>
<p begin="13714300000t" end="13759300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">快點回家去吧  揮舞著袖子</p>
<p begin="13767700000t" end="13864800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">お魚を焼く匂い　晩ご飯のいい匂い</p>
<p begin="13767700000t" end="13864800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">烤魚的味道  晚飯的香味</p>
<p begin="13874000000t" end="13919900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">お腹の虫も泣きだした</p>
<p begin="13874000000t" end="13919900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">肚裡的蛔蟲  也開始咕咕叫</p>
<p begin="13925700000t" end="13972900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">意地を張りのも　飽きてきた</p>
<p begin="13925700000t" end="13972900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">也差不多厭倦賭氣了</p>
<p begin="13978700000t" end="14024200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">今すぐごめん　と謝って</p>
<p begin="13978700000t" end="14024200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">現在立刻道歉認錯吧</p>
<p begin="14025800000t" end="14080500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">あぁ　速くお家に帰りたい</p>
<p begin="14025800000t" end="14080500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">快點回到家裡吧</p>
<p begin="14135100000t" end="14230200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">在這蛋痛的城鎮觀光 !</p>
<p begin="14135100000t" end="14230200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">親愛的  富尼弗拉  鈍鈍子</p>
<p begin="14141200000t" end="14163500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">親愛的  富尼弗拉  鈍鈍子</p>
<p begin="14165200000t" end="14180600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">謝謝你們的回信</p>
<p begin="14182900000t" end="14194900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">我很健康</p>
<p begin="14198500000t" end="14221200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">關於上一封信上的夥伴們</p>
<p begin="14221300000t" end="14230200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">他們是實際存在…</p>
